    🟢 Performance Concerns

     1. Unnecessary allocations - GetEvents() copies entire slice on every call
     2. Repeated config copies - cfg.RawCopy() called frequently
     3. Inefficient string concatenation - Multiple ReplaceAll calls instead of strings.Builder
     4. Blocking file operations in HTTP handlers - No timeout or context cancellation

